src: Tierra del Sol is pleased to present "Vicente Siso: Memories of the Land and Water" at the new gallery location in West Hollywood. Siso has been an artist in the Studio Arts Program since 2012, this marks his debut solo exhibition. Siso was born 1962 in Madrid and raised between Venezuela, Trinidad and Miami; he moved with his family to Southern California in his early 20s.
ref: Tierra del Sol se complace en presentar "Vicente Siso: Recuerdos de la tierra y el agua" en la nueva ubicación de esta galería, en West Hollywood. Siso lleva siendo un artista del Studio Arts Program desde 2012, y este evento marca su debut en una exposición en solitario. Siso nació en Madrid en 1962 y se crió entre Venezuela, Trinidad y Miami. A los 20 años se muda con su familia al sur de California.

src: The Tierra del Sol Gallery is located at 7414 Santa Monica Blvd. For information, visit tierradelsolgallery.org.
ref: La galería Tierra del Sol se encuentra en el 7414 de Santa Mónica Blvd. Para más información, visita tierradelsolgallery.org.

src: Over the past decade, our lives have changed through technology, with many working from home, and Sydney has gained an impressive network of metro and light rail systems. Our ability to purchase online has changed the way we shop, and friends and family seem closer because of smartphone communication. All of these adaptations from one system to another can also occur in our built environment through a planning focus on adaptive reuse rather than preferencing heritage preservation.
ref: A lo largo de la pasada década nuestras vidas han cambiado gracias a la tecnología, donde muchos trabajan desde casa, y Sídney se ha dotado de una impresionante red de metro y tren ligero. El poder comprar por Internet ha cambiado, precisamente, nuestra forma de comprar, y los amigos y la familia parecen estar más cerca gracias a la comunicación vía smartphone. Todas estas adaptaciones de un sistema a otro pueden producirse, también, en nuestro entorno construido a través de una planificación centrada en la reutilización adaptativa, en vez de dar preferencia a la conservación del patrimonio.

src: Last year, the World Economic Forum forecast that it would take five generations to achieve gender equality in every nation. Now the World Bank wants to rapidly accelerate that time frame.
ref: El año pasado, el Foro Económico Mundial pronosticó que harían falta cinco generaciones para lograr la igualdad de género en todas las naciones. Ahora, el Banco Mundial quiere acelerar ese plazo rápidamente.

src: More than 99% of the domestic wine sector is made up of micro- to medium-sized companies, Sánchez Recarte said, questioning the solidity of legal arguments made by brewers and asserting that his organisation had focused on presenting policy makers with information "relevant and appropriate" to its own industry.

src: An 83-hour wait in a hospital A&E; four-in-ten patients waiting longer than four hours; 30 ambulances queuing outside a hospital, unable to respond to other emergency calls; staff "leaving shifts in tears" over the standard of care and "a near collapse of performance," according to an expert at the Royal College of Emergency Medicine.
ref: Una espera de 83 horas en urgencias, cuatro de cada diez pacientes esperando más de cuatro horas, 30 ambulancias haciendo cola fuera de un hospital, incapacidad de atender otras llamadas de emergencia, personal "finalizando su turno entre lágrimas" debido al nivel de atención y un "colapso casi total del rendimiento de las prestaciones", según un experto del Royal College of Emergency Medicine.

src: Independent oversight will promote public trust and data-driven decision-making in a field that has for too long operated without the benefit of transparency. We ask the Legislature to enact into law our task force's recommendation to restore independent oversight of our state's city, county, and regional jails. People's lives depend on it.
ref: La supervisión independiente promovería la confianza pública y la toma de decisiones basada en datos en un ámbito que durante mucho tiempo ha operado al margen de la transparencia. Pedimos al poder legislativo que convierta en ley la recomendación de nuestro grupo de trabajo de restaurar la supervisión independiente en nuestro estado de nuestras cárceles municipales, comarcales y regionales. La vida de las personas depende de ello.

src: It's important to keep in mind that, even though these rates are per million departures, some of the plane models in this report - for example, the Boeing 727 introduced in 1964 - have been around for decades and consequently had much longer to accumulate an accident record than others.

src: Independent oversight will promote public trust and data-driven decision-making in a field that has for too long operated without the benefit of transparency.
